title: Part 10 of the Dutch top 2000 of 2007
description:
Well, here it is, the final part! I hope you enjoyed it. I would like to thank Sjoerd for supplying the list with the rankings of the previous years.
Please comment on any mistakes you&#039;ve found, it is impossible to keep track of all these 2000 songs. So if you find any wrong versions, bad songs, number errors, let me know.
I wish you all a lot of listening pleasure. Enjoy!
